Package: DISCOURSE
Title: Data-simulation via Iterative Stochastic Combinatorial Optimization Using Reported Summary Estimates
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sebastian A. J.", "Lortz", , "s.a.j.lortz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: We introduce the DISCOURSE framework – Data-simulation via Iterative Stochastic Combinatorial Optimization Using Reported Summary Estimates.
  This algorithmic framework is designed to reconstruct complete data sets solely from summary statistics.
  It provides researchers with a tool to inform the discourse when raw data are unavailable, thereby informing decision‑making in replication studies.
